'''Hosidius guards''' can be found around [[Hosidius]], in [[Great Kourend]]. In most ways, they act like common [[guard]]s, sharing the same drops and being pickpocketable at level 40 [[Thieving]] for the same 30 [[coins]] and 46.5 Thieving [[experience]]. However, unlike regular guards, some Hosidius guards are equipped with bows, and thus attack with range.

